description:
Bigfoot “Peace and Solidarity” Collection is a NFT collection based on the lengendary bigfoot character from the owner’s hometown of western Canada.  Inspired by “Fall Guys” artwork, the “Peace and Solidarity” Collection is 3,350 unique digital collectibles.  The collection represents our collective protest and solidarity against racism.  

Each collectible has a distinct set of colors to highlight our uniqueness but also take from a similar design, to highlight how we’re also, all the same.  In this collection, Bigfoot symbolizes friendliness, righteousness and how we are all capable of leaving a “big footprint” on the world.    

The collection was created based on six core designs to represent the human population across the six out of the seven total continents in the world where humans reside with the rest, replicated programmatically, similar to human reproduction.  This collection is an experiment in generative art to promote peace around the world.
name: Bigfoot - Peace and Solidarity Collection
